fields.Title: SEAFORT / MATTRESS NEST
fields.Description: (in front of double embrasure looking over the bay, into whirling window, ends check island task, shot was made here)

fields.Title: Composure: "Then again... his face twitches."
fields.Dialogue Text: Then again... his face twitches.

fields.Title: Jump to: [You: "Is the shooter still here?"]
Logic: "A good place to hide. Relatively sa..."
fields.Dialogue Text: A good place to hide. Relatively safe from the snow and the rain...

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""This looks like a good place to ai..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "This looks like a good place to aim from..." The lieutenant looks around. He steps closer with his hand on his gun.

fields.Title: You: ""Finally.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Finally."

fields.Title: You: "...but not with 100% certainty."
fields.Dialogue Text: ...but not with 100% certainty.

fields.Title: Shivers: "In the North, something moves. Leav..."
fields.Dialogue Text: In the North, something moves. Leaving circles on the water. Long stalks in the shallows...

fields.Title: You: ""On this island.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "On this island."

fields.Title: Shivers: "YES."
fields.Dialogue Text: YES.

fields.Title: Cuno: ""You see someone here?" He points t..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "You see someone here?" He points to the mattress. "Fuckin' invisible shooter? Spooky shit..."

fields.Title: You: ""Cuno, with a pair of binoculars, I..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Cuno, with a pair of binoculars, I would be able to see *inside* the room."

fields.Title: Mattress Nest: "A towering skyscraper, its top floo..."
fields.Dialogue Text: A towering skyscraper, its top floors shaved off by artillery fire -- Capeside Apartments: Rue de Saint Ghislaine 33A and 33B.

fields.Title: You: ""Someone's been smoking Tioumoutiri..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Someone's been smoking Tioumoutiri cigarettes."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: "He does not answer, just nods. With..."
fields.Dialogue Text: He does not answer, just nods. With his back hunched, he looks around once more and says...

fields.Title: You: ""You think he's here?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "You think he's here?"

fields.Title: You: ""In Martinaise.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "In Martinaise."

fields.Title: You: ""On this island.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "On this island."

fields.Title: You: ""Yes -- there's an opening between..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yes -- there's an opening between 33A and 10. I can see to the roof."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Yes. This guy gets around.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yes. This guy gets around."

fields.Title: Mattress Nest: "The box-shaped silhouette of the Wh..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The box-shaped silhouette of the Whirling-in-Rags. Its sloped roof. A tiny fleck of light catches your eye on the rooftop -- sunlight reflecting off the upstairs window of Klaasje's room.
fields.Alternate1: The box-shaped silhouette of the Whirling-in-Rags. You see the rooftop at night -- the upstairs window of Klaasje's room reflecting a streetlamp outside.
fields.Alternate2: The box-shaped silhouette of the Whirling-in-Rags. You see a small fleck of white on the rooftop -- the upstairs window of Klaasje's room in the rain, reflecting light.
fields.Alternate3: The box-shaped silhouette of the Whirling-in-Rags. You see a small fleck of white on the rooftop -- the upstairs window of Klaasje's room in the snow, reflecting light.

fields.Title: You: "I don't want to boast..."
fields.Dialogue Text: I don't want to boast...

fields.Title: You: ""Boo-yah. Master cop work.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Boo-yah. Master cop work."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""We will make up for it. Here. I fe..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "We will make up for it. Here. I feel it."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""No, officer. It's not an *invisibl..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "No, officer. It's not an *invisible* shooter. But..." He lowers his voice even further. "This island, on the other hand..."

fields.Title: You: ""Our shooter's a heavy smoker.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Our shooter's a heavy smoker."

fields.Title: You: "Touch the concrete first."
fields.Dialogue Text: Touch the concrete first.

fields.Title: You: "On the left..."
fields.Dialogue Text: On the left...

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Do you have line of sight to the w..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Do you have line of sight to the window?"

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Good." He pats you on the back, th..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Good." He pats you on the back, three small pats in a row. "I think we have it, detective. The origin of the shot. This is the *sniper's nest*."

fields.Title: You: ""You're right.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "You're right."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Where?" He looks behind his back."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Where?" He looks behind his back.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Or *she*." He almost whispers. "We..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Or *she*." He almost whispers. "We should move."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""B triple prime..." The lieutenant..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "B triple prime..." The lieutenant lowers his voice, stepping closer with his hand on his gun. "This looks like a good place to shoot from."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""I can see it," he nods. "Through t..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I can see it," he nods. "Through the scope of a rifle. The shooter would be prone, lying on the mattress, barrel resting on the embrasure."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: "He nods. "Nothing pointed here -- m..."
fields.Dialogue Text: He nods. "Nothing pointed here -- many leads pointed elsewhere."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Motherfucker?" He sounds excited...."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Motherfucker?" He sounds excited. "You seein' the window or not?"

fields.Title: Visual Calculus: "No. You feel there's something impo..."
fields.Dialogue Text: No. You feel there's something important here.  The embrasure. Look again...

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""In our defence -- nothing pointed..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "In our defence -- nothing pointed here. Many, many leads pointed elsewhere."

fields.Title: You: "Inspect the mattress."
fields.Dialogue Text: Inspect the mattress.

fields.Title: You: "And between the two..."
fields.Dialogue Text: And between the two...

fields.Title: You: ""Kim, with a pair of binoculars, I..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Kim, with a pair of binoculars, I would be able to see *inside* the room."

fields.Title: You: ""Could the shooter still be... here?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Could the shooter still be... here?"

dialogueEntries.conditionsString: Variable["seafort.nest_concrete_hole_checked"] == true  and  (IsKimHere()  or  IsCunoInParty())  and  Variable["seafort.deserter_prehub_reached"] == false

fields.Title: You: ""There it is.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "There it is."

fields.Title: Jump to: [You: ""Could the shooter still be... here?""]
Mattress Nest: "The springs screech as you lean on..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The springs screech as you lean on the mattress and crane your neck to look out...

fields.Title: You: "Back off."
fields.Dialogue Text: Back off.

fields.Title: You: "On the right..."
fields.Dialogue Text: On the right...

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Don't beat yourself up, officer. W..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Don't beat yourself up, officer. We did not put guns in their hands, or get them drunk." He looks north, over the fortification, then adds:

fields.Title: You: "I could take the shot."
fields.Dialogue Text: I could take the shot.

fields.Title: You: "This is where the shot came from..."
fields.Dialogue Text: This is where the shot came from...

fields.Title: Conceptualization: "Perhaps it's a..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Perhaps it's a...

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""I have always assumed it's someone..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I have always assumed it's someone local." He nods.

fields.Title: Jump to: [Mattress Nest: "A rain-soaked mattress on a concret..."]
Cuno: ""Yeah, detective Cuno thinks it's s..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yeah, detective Cuno thinks it's some local asshole too. These people are rats..."

fields.Title: You: ""Tioumoutiri. Like the ones we foun..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Tioumoutiri. Like the ones we found at Land's End, remember?"

fields.Title: Jump to: [Mattress Nest: "A rain-soaked mattress on a concret..."]
Perception (Sight): "More than that."
fields.Dialogue Text: More than that.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""No, wait." He points to the embras..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "No, wait." He points to the embrasure. "This is important, I have a feeling... What can you see?"

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""I think we have it. The origin of..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I think we have it. The origin of the shot -- this is the *sniper's nest*." He pats you on the back, three small pats in a row.

fields.Title: You: ""In Martinaise.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "In Martinaise."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""You think so?" he whispers, pointi..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "You think so?" he whispers, pointing to the mattress. "We would *see* them if they were here."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""We should move. Now.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "We should move. Now."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Where?" Cuno looks around the smal..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Where?" Cuno looks around the small compartment-sized room.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Why not? We have the weapon and ba..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Why not? We have the weapon and ballistics. As you say it's..." He looks north, over the fortification. "Pretty *boo-yah*."

fields.Title: Jump to: [You: ""Could the shooter still be... here?""]
Mattress Nest: "A small piece of Martinaise coastli..."
fields.Dialogue Text: A small piece of Martinaise coastline opens up in the square in front of you -- like a tiny landscape painting, one kilometre across the water. The ruins look familiar.
fields.Alternate1: A small piece of Martinaise coastline opens up in the square in front of you, like a tiny landscape painting, one kilometre across the water. Dead in the centre is the Whirling-in-Rags.

fields.Title: Electrochemistry: "Whenever you wanted. Like your own..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Whenever you wanted. Like your own little dollhouse...

fields.Title: You: ""*Why* didn't we come here before?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "*Why* didn't we come here before?"

fields.Title: Visual Calculus: "This is B triple prime -- on the is..."
fields.Dialogue Text: This is B triple prime -- on the island... A nest.

fields.Title: Perception (Sight): "And an empty can of beans on the gr..."
fields.Dialogue Text: And an empty can of beans on the ground next to it -- filled to the brim with cigarette butts.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Why? We don't go everywhere in a t..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Why? We don't go everywhere in a thousand metre radius of the crime scene. That's not procedure."

fields.Title: You: ""Someone's been smoking Tioumoutiri..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Someone's been smoking Tioumoutiri cigarettes. Not a lot of that around."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""I may have been wrong -- when I sa..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I may have been wrong -- when I said it was unimportant." He stares into the can for a second. "This means the same person could have visited both locations."

fields.Title: Jump to: [Kim Kitsuragi: ""I think we have it. The origin of..."]
Cuno: ""Let's get a move on. We're out in..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Let's get a move on. We're out in the open here..."

fields.Title: Perception (Sight): "The silhouette of a tobacco picker..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The silhouette of a tobacco picker adorns the paper filter. The brand: Tioumoutiri.

fields.Title: You: ""I saw the same brand of cigarettes..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I saw the same brand of cigarettes extinguished in Land's End." (Point west.)

fields.Title: Perception (Sight): "What are you talking about -- "Can'..."
fields.Dialogue Text: What are you talking about -- "Can't be certain?" It's certain.

fields.Title: You: ""Better late than never.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Better late than never."

fields.Title: Mattress Nest: "The wind blows suddenly. The clear..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The wind blows suddenly. The clear surface of the water shudders. Yes. This is it.

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Someone been hidin' here like a bi..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Someone been hidin' here like a bitch," he whispers. "Maybe  jerkin' off too?"

fields.Title: You: ""An old man's brand of cigarettes....."
fields.Dialogue Text: "An old man's brand of cigarettes...."

fields.Title: Reaction Speed: "The same rare brand... from Land's..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The same rare brand... from Land's End, before. Interesting.

fields.Title: Jump to: [You: ""Could the shooter still be... here?""]
Mattress Nest: "A single-person mattress. Modern, c..."
fields.Dialogue Text: A single-person mattress. Modern, civilian use. Brand name: Marjorie. There's a fuel stain on the cover, along with cigarette burns.

fields.Title: Mattress Nest: "The red chimney and collapsed rear..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The red chimney and collapsed rear wall of the four-story tenement in front of the Whirling-in-Rags -- Rue de Saint Ghislaine 10.
fields.Alternate1: The red chimney and collapsed back of the four-story tenement in front of the Whirling-in-Rags -- Rue de Saint Ghislaine 10. The Doomed Commercial Area.

fields.Title: You: ""Motherfucker.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Motherfucker."

fields.Title: Inland Empire: "Trepidation. A tingling feeling in..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Trepidation. A tingling feeling in your stomach...

fields.Title: You: ""Kim, I could make it -- I could ma..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Kim, I could make it -- I could make the shot."

fields.Title: You: ""Tioumoutiri. Like the ones we foun..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Tioumoutiri. Like the ones we found at Land's End, remember?"

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Could be a coincidence. Or -- the..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Could be a coincidence. Or -- the same person has visited Land's End and..." He looks around, "...here."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""You see the window or not?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "You see the window or not?"

fields.Title: Jump to: [Mattress Nest: "The springs screech as you lean on..."]
You: "Pick one out of the can."
fields.Dialogue Text: Pick one out of the can.

fields.Title: You: ""I can't be 100% certain, but...""
fields.Dialogue Text: "I can't be 100% certain, but..."

fields.Title: You: ""Yes -- there's an opening between..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yes -- there's an opening between 33A and 10. I can see to the roof."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Anything?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Anything?"

fields.Title: You: "Say nothing, drop the cigarette bac..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Say nothing, drop the cigarette back into the can.

fields.Title: Half Light: "He feels... uncomfortable suddenly."
fields.Dialogue Text: He feels... uncomfortable suddenly.

fields.Title: Half Light: "He feels... uncomfortable suddenly."
fields.Dialogue Text: He feels... uncomfortable suddenly.

fields.Title: You: "Inspect the wall."
fields.Dialogue Text: Inspect the wall.
fields.Alternate1: Inspect the wall through which the shot was made again.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""What? Do you have line of sight to..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "What? Do you have line of sight to the window?"

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""I didn't see any signs of smoking..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I didn't see any signs of smoking inside, though. If people live there, they keep it tidy -- this here may also be a smoking spot."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""A good place to hide. Cosy. Relati..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "A good place to hide. Cosy. Relatively safe from the rain..." He pokes the mattress.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""What does that mean? Do you have l..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "What does that mean? Do you have line of sight to the window?"

fields.Title: Mattress Nest: "The wind picks up slowly. The clear..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The wind picks up slowly. The clear surface of the water shudders. Yes. This is it.

fields.Title: Perception (Sight): "What are you talking about -- "Can'..."
fields.Dialogue Text: What are you talking about -- "Can't be certain?"

fields.Title: You: ""Right *here*.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Right *here*."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Right fucking on." He stops. A shu..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Right fucking on." He stops. A shudder.

fields.Title: You: "Got you. [Leave.]"
fields.Dialogue Text: Got you. [Leave.]

fields.Title: Hand/Eye Coordination: "Cheek against the cheek rest, hand..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Cheek against the cheek rest, hand on the hair trigger. On a calm day like this...

fields.Title: You: ""Right *here*." (Point at the mattr..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Right *here*." (Point at the mattress.)

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""But." He lowers his voice again. "..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "But." He lowers his voice again. "This island on the other hand..."

fields.Title: Mattress Nest: "No answer comes. Not even a whisper..."
fields.Dialogue Text: No answer comes. Not even a whisper on the water.

fields.Title: Cuno: ""There what is, the window?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "There what is, the window?"

fields.Title: Perception (Sight): "More than that."
fields.Dialogue Text: More than that.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""A pair of binoculars? Or a scope o..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "A pair of binoculars? Or a scope of a *rifle*?" He points to the makeshift bed. "You'd be prone, lying on the mattress, barrel resting on the embrasure..."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Noted." The lieutenant stares into..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Noted." The lieutenant stares into the can for a second.

fields.Title: Visual Calculus: "Affirmative."
fields.Dialogue Text: Affirmative.

fields.Title: Mattress Nest: "Quite old, and grimy from years wit..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Quite old, and grimy from years without cleaning by anything other than the rain.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""That embrasure... What can you see..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "That embrasure... What can you see through it?"

fields.Title: You: "[Turn away.]"
fields.Dialogue Text: [Turn away.]

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: "He nods. "The smoker's a clean pers..."
fields.Dialogue Text: He nods. "The smoker's a clean person. I didn't see any signs of smoking inside. Keeps it tidy -- prefers to come out here to smoke."

fields.Title: You: ""Six people are dead. We could have..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Six people are dead. We could have prevented it."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""It's only *moderately* effective c..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "It's only *moderately* effective cop work until we have the weapon. It will not be, how do you say it..." He looks north, over the fortification. "*Boo-yah*, until we have that..."

fields.Title: You: ""Motherfucker.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Motherfucker."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""No, but what about..." He points t..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "No, but what about..." He points to the embrasure. "What's out there?"

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Yes. It all adds up." He stares in..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yes. It all adds up." He stares into the can for a second.

fields.Title: Mattress Nest: "There's a firing slit in the wall i..."
fields.Dialogue Text: There's a firing slit in the wall in front of you. Like a little window...

fields.Title: Mattress Nest: "There's a rain-soaked mattress on a..."
fields.Dialogue Text: There's a rain-soaked mattress on a concrete slab, only half-covered by the crumbling roof. At the head of it -- double embrasures -- firing slits, like two eyes in the wall.

fields.Title: You: "Look through the hole in the concre..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Look through the hole in the concrete.

fields.Title: You: ""There it is.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "There it is."

fields.Title: Encyclopedia: "Contemporary Revacholians prefer Dr..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Contemporary Revacholians prefer Drouin (a local blend from the southern islands) or Astra, the legendary cigarette from Graad. Tioumoutiri is favoured by older men for its paper filter tips, sweet smell, and added tar.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: "He looks north, over the fortificat..."
fields.Dialogue Text: He looks north, over the fortification. Then at the mattress.

fields.Title: Empathy: "The lieutenant pauses. Regret comes..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The lieutenant pauses. Regret comes over him.

fields.Title: Empathy: "He's conflicted for a second. There..."
fields.Dialogue Text: He's conflicted for a second. There's guilt there, it takes him a moment to rationalize it away.

fields.Title: You: "Is the shooter still here?"
fields.Dialogue Text: Is the shooter still here?

dialogueEntries.conditionsString: Variable["seafort.nest_concrete_hole_checked"] == true  and  IsKimHere() == false  and  IsCunoInParty() == false  and  Variable["seafort.deserter_prehub_reached"] == false

fields.Title: Mattress Nest: "A rain-soaked mattress on a concret..."
fields.Dialogue Text: A rain-soaked mattress on a concrete slab. In front of it -- double embrasures -- firing slits like two eyes in the wall.

fields.Title: You: ""I can't be 100% certain, but...""
fields.Dialogue Text: "I can't be 100% certain, but..."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Cuno fucking knew it. This a snipe..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Cuno fucking knew it. This a sniper's nest, right? Fuckin' assassin action... Cuno *barely* understands what's happening -- but he likes the shit out of it."

fields.Title: Hand/Eye Coordination: "Cheek against the cheek rest, hand..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Cheek against the cheek rest, hand on the hair trigger. On a calm day like this...

fields.Title: You: ""Someone's been smoking here.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Someone's been smoking here."
